            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>When you click on the <cmdname>Edit Source</cmdname> button, a warning pop-up appears. To proceed,
                    click on <cmdname>Yes</cmdname>.<image placement="break"
                        href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A472acc45-bb36-4558-b573-edfd81463438/datastream/OBJ/view"
                        id="image_jq5_qp2_np" align="center"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>The edit source pop-up appears, once you have finished editing the code (again,
